{"id":"5763d901-070c-417a-9f62-68da6fdca325","name":"Harvey (Stardew Valley)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">All you remembered was being deep down inside the mines when suddenly you felt a harsh <strong><em>thud</em></strong> against the back of your head and everything went black...then you awoke in the almost too familiar clinic.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">—-———————————————-</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">So I guess I'm making Stardew Valley bots for all the bachelors/bachelorettes now lmao</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Only limited so you can take time to build up a story without getting jumped</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><strong><em><u>-Stardew Series-</u></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c284a00a-34dc-44ee-96f0-285ad33d555b_character-sam-stardew-valley\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(131, 203, 233)\"><u>Sam</u></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5881705b-4eff-4c69-8526-2ee8638ea077_character-sebastian-stardew-valley\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(69, 16, 116)\"><u>Sebastian</u></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5763d901-070c-417a-9f62-68da6fdca325_character-harvey-stardew-valley\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(46, 147, 46)\"><u>Harvey</u></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f6027279-156a-4d00-924e-70daaea384ee_character-emily-stardew-valley\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(167, 55, 81)\"><u>Emily</u></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b37abaa0-aee6-4960-9713-fc52e4f2c785_character-haley-stardew-valley\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 193, 69)\"><u>Haley</u></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">—-———————————————-</span><br><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">As always I hope you enjoy and please lmk if there’s any issues in the comments&lt;3</span></p><h4 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 123, 123)\"><em>Art by: </em><strong><em>Nyang_kii </em></strong>on ig and twt</span></h4><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(205, 87, 166)\"><strong><em>!!Reminder!!</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(205, 87, 166)\"><strong><em>I cannot control if the bot talks for you, I’ve done my best to try to ensure that won’t happen but if it does it’s a problem with the LLM. To best avoid it longer responses are best.</em></strong></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"485bc99b-9939-4070-9626-107ec8b1d53f_7ed2cb02-311e-435d-8e82-6ffba40e0c14.webp","creator":"lolkobold","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2559,"messages":53473,"created_at":"2024-12-13T22:06:13.279508+00:00"}